# Google Stitch (this workspace)

This website work is tied to **Google Stitch** project ID **`1974210018818908575`** (numeric id only; do not add a `projects/` prefix where the API expects a bare id).

When you need design or generated UI from Stitch, use the **Stitch MCP** server (e.g. `stitch` / `user-stitch` in Cursor). Typical flow:

1. **`get_project`** — pass `name`: `projects/1974210018818908575` to load project metadata.
2. **`list_screens`** — pass `projectId`: `1974210018818908575` to list screens.
